token_info.name: Giant Squid
token_info.description: This OBJKT is inspired by the novel “Sphere” from the brilliant mind of Michael Crichton. It is a representation of the fear that is lurking deep in the subconscious of our minds. It is a deep-dwelling creature. It has been thought that Giant Squids extinct. However, plenty of squid beaks were found in the stomachs of stranded or hunted whales. It’s impossible to count Giant Squids. But their number can be extrapolated from the number of sperm whales (the squid’s primary predator).
